    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I use this bash functions to open vim with splits for each file in which grep or rak find the pattern I'm searching for:
```bash
grepvim(){
  grep -rl "$1" $2| xargs mvim -o +/"$1"
}</p>

<p>rakvim(){
  rak -l "$1" $2| xargs mvim -o +/"$1"
}
```</p>
